                        <td>
                            
                            <b> ANC.DT.16 Dietary counselling:</b> 
                            
                            <br/>
                            
                            <b>When:</b>
                            
                            <i>Named Event:</i> ANC.B10. Counselling, in-facility management &amp; treatment 
                            <br/>
                            
                            
                            
                            
                            <b>Then:</b>
                            <table class="grid-dict">
                                
                                <tr>
                                    <td>
                                        
                                        Increase daily energy and protein intake to reduce the risk of low-birth-weight neonates

[Protein Sources and Energy Sources]
                                        
                                        <br/>
                                        
                                        
                                        <b>If:</b>
                                        
                                        <i>Applicability:</i>
                                        
                                        (&quot;Population prevalence of undernourishment&quot; ≥ 20%)
  AND (&quot;Weight category&quot; = &quot;Underweight&quot;)
                                        
                                        <i>(Should Conduct counselling on dietary interventions)</i>
                                        <br/>
                                        
                                        
                                        
                                        <b>Then:</b> <i>Additional sub-actions not displayed</i>
                                        
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                
                                <tr>
                                    <td>
                                        
                                        Balanced energy and protein dietary supplementation is recommended for pregnant women to reduce the risk of stillbirths and small-for-gestational-age neonates
                                        
                                        <br/>
                                        
                                        
                                        <b>If:</b>
                                        
                                        <i>Applicability:</i>
                                        
                                        (&quot;Population prevalence of undernourishment&quot; ≥ 20%)
  AND (&quot;Weight category&quot; = &quot;Underweight&quot;)
                                        
